# WhisperApp Architecture

## System Overview
```
User Hand Gestures
    ↓
Leap Motion Controller (120 FPS)
    ↓
Hardware Layer (app/hardware/)
    ↓
Preprocessing Pipeline (app/core/preprocessing.py)
    ↓
AI Service (app/services/model_service.py)
    ↓
UI Layer (app/ui/)
    ↓
Display Recognition Results
```

## Module Responsibilities

### 1. `app/hardware/`
- **leap_controller.py**: Interface with Leap Motion SDK
- **stream_manager.py**: Manage real-time data stream

### 2. `app/core/`
- **preprocessing.py**: Normalize, smooth skeletal data
- **buffer.py**: Circular buffer for streaming data
- **config.py**: App configuration management

### 3. `app/services/`
- **model_service.py**: Load & run WhisperSign model
- **inference_service.py**: Handle batch/streaming inference
- **result_manager.py**: Post-process predictions

### 4. `app/ui/`
- **main_window.py**: Main GUI window
- **visualization.py**: Real-time skeleton visualization
- **controls.py**: Start/stop, settings buttons

### 5. `app/utils/`
- **logger.py**: Logging utility
- **metrics.py**: Performance monitoring